com.facebook.buck.core.rules.provider

Class BuildRuleInfoProviderCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.rules.provider.BuildRuleInfoProviderCollection

  • public final class BuildRuleInfoProviderCollection
extends Object
    A container for storing a collection of BuildRuleInfoProvider for BuildRule. This is basically a wrapper around an ImmutableMap that provides more convenient provider access and building.

    The supplied BuildRuleProviderCollection must contain DefaultBuildRuleInfoProvider or MissingProviderException will be thrown
